de.humatic.dsj.com

Class IMpeg2PIDMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.humatic.dsj.com.COMObject
      • de.humatic.dsj.com.IMpeg2PIDMap

  • public class IMpeg2PIDMap
extends COMObject
    Wrapper around the native IMpeg2PIDMap interface exposed by output pins on Microsoft's demultiplexer in transportstream mode.
    To get an instance of this class, call COMFactory.queryInterface(...) with the pin of interest and COMFactory.IID_IMpeg2PIDMap as arguments.
    For more information see MSDN documentation.
